NAME
        leave - leave a team

SYNOPSIS
	leave
        leave team
	leave <person>


DESCRIPTION
        This command is used when you want to leave a team, or if you
	want to exclude a member in the team that you lead.
	Leaving a team will automatically put you into verbose mode again
	if entering the team made you switch to brief mode.

OPTIONS
        [none] - leave the team you are a member of

	person - a member of the team you lead

	'team' - Leave the team you are a member of.  If you are the
	         team's leader, the team is completely disbanded.

SEE ALSO
	invite, join, options, team, teams
	For general information, see teams
